patchomv (1.4.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * additional patch to allow spaces in share names, because the maintainer of OMV does everything to force
    his wierd opinion that Samba share names should not contain spaces on every user.
    Samba has handled spaces in share names without any problems for ages. So it's ridiculous what OMV does here.

